{"tid":2089343,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[BNO平權] 身為一個00後，有小小野想講","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T03:08:10.000Z","uid":201142,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"af21b888c6f448b0c7a9ab7c038de3c3362855c5","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"面對支共極權的打壓，如今香港危在旦夕，今天英國首相Boris Johnson稱國安法嚴重違反一國兩制，宣布將會安排BNO持有人到英國定居，計劃將會於數月後實施。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個個都走，咁香港點算？<br />\n班97後00後冇BNO嘅手足點算？<br />\n唔係話要光復香港咩？依家話走？<br />\n原來移民係唯一出路？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我嘅睇法係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得走一定要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我確實睇唔到香港重光既未來，因地緣政治因素，就如我之前開過嘅post所寫，「一日支共政權仲存在，香港一日都唔會重光到」，呢個係香港重光必須fulfill嘅前題，而呢樣野亦冇可能在數十年內做到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身為一個00後，書又未讀完，錢又冇，藍絲老豆港豬老母又冇攞BNO，成撚日開住個33台睇CCTV，走係絕對要靠自己，但我絕對支持擁有BNO嘅手足們一定要走，但唔係要你哋從此放棄抗爭，<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係組成國際大包圍網圍堵支共政權，再重回呢片熟悉嘅土地。人哋以色列人民被迫逃離故鄉流散各地，數千年後都可以重新立國，我地香港人為何不可以？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得走，一定要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n唔使擔心我哋架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e5e8c6b58e550f4ba9f7045ea2018d30329d91","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd143c053b3cf9225ed60dc5b3aa4bc707f28bfd","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91d7209ae351151500c3c0bd2e19bb1b12c0a957","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68ea782b4f1727aa0b1ab51e194bbe408941d96f","tid":2089343,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58c838c12e59ffdc8bd079aef87388db9308278f","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"樓主係移民撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fbb3390d137f51f35ce2d765cd4ea7d73fb887","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"062b4a4a371e3f4cd22b3c873cf7de3e21c6a532","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0aac88f657a3900ec9841ed86089e7dbfa31971c","tid":2089343,"uid":201142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主垃圾冇用鬼"},{"pid":"cf9da436508b961bed143605f7040611350032a3","tid":2089343,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:26:23.000Z","msg":"滾動<br />\n申利: 冇 BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd820d3f9bd823ff6fb7418d63045905b4b0aaf7","tid":2089343,"uid":199845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"推 多謝你CHING 我都係00"},{"pid":"84001d8d7cca4a015111025ffea2b2f45ff19780","tid":2089343,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"走得就走，要你做外國文宣，要你參軍<br />\n要打解放軍果陣，你係先鋒"},{"pid":"c57643445317a1a1eebad77cae1d228dcdb2d731","tid":2089343,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化<br />\n無論點都會為咪走到既手足繼續爭取啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394f4a7f373eacbf9a8aa7d85ae90c365bfd301c","tid":2089343,"uid":11